{"title":"父亲·菜园","authors":["李贤"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲·菜园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李贤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲在菜园里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如白云飘游在蓝天里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成一幅剪影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲摇动起辘轳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把清水倒进菜畦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——是一股涌动的心血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇灌素淡的心情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲的汗珠掉进井底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一声清脆的嗓音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊动井底的蛙叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年四季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲都在菜园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认真地为这个瓜那条藤搭架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些藤沿着父亲的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长出花香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长出鸟鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们这些远离父亲的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被菜园的藤蔓牵着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感觉父亲的爱也是绿色的"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}